'''Ed King''' is a [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] letterer. He worked on the [[Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (Marvel Comics 1983)|''Star Wars: Return of the Jedi'']] comics, as well as [[Droids (1986) 8|''Droids'' (1986) 8]] and [[Star Wars (1977) 98|''Star Wars'' (1977) 98]].

